    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a dependable commuter for many years. While the engine and transmission remain solid, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including several visible scratches, some minor door dings, and patches of clear coat oxidation on the roof and trunk. The interior is functional but shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. It is a practical choice for someone looking for a reliable budget-friendly option who doesn't mind some cosmetic imperfections.",
