      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in a car that\u2019s full of character and ready for its next chapter! This dependable ride is in fair condition, showing some honest signs of its journey so far, but it remains a solid and functional choice for anyone looking for value. It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a reliable vehicle that still has plenty of life left to give!",
