      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, currently offered in commendable condition. This specimen exhibits a consistent history of professional care, ensuring robust mechanical integrity and a refined aesthetic presence. Having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, it stands as a testament to durability and sustained performance. This is an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a reliable, high-caliber vehicle at a competitive valuation.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
