      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks sharp on the road. It runs super smoothly and is totally ready for its next big adventure. I've taken great care of it, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 3.2L displacement that sings to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. This example has had critical preventive maintenance addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system refresh, ensuring the chassis handles the torque loads without fatigue. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and telepathic feedback characteristic of this platform. While the exterior shows honest wear from spirited driving, the drivetrain is dialed in and ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs well. Serious buyers only.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a well-maintained, reliable driver. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss shine, with only minor, expected road wear such as small stone chips on the front fascia that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seating is supple and free of any punctures or significant stains, showing only light characteristic creasing on the driver's side bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the heated seats and navigation, has been tested and is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, paired with a transmission that shifts smoothly through all gears. We have recently performed a comprehensive multi-point inspection, confirmed the brakes have plenty of life remaining, and ensured the tires are in excellent shape with deep tread. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, offering a refined driving experience that feels tight and responsive on the road.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
